1�The ancient bane...The Shadow of Darkness--an image of the Shadow Lord--told us...that our kinds were the ones that had awakened him.
1�That he would spread the bane that will destroy Vana'diel from our cowardice, rage, envy, arrogance, and apathy...
1�??But as one bright star shines through the clouds at night, and as one song rings clear above the roar of beasts, we hold to one hope in these darkest of times.??
1�??That they will come, with the wisdom of ages and the strength of thousands, to deliver us from our plight. We await the awakening of the Warriors of the Crystal.??
1�That's an old song... It's called ??The Warriors of the Crystal,?? isn't it?
1�Thirty years ago, the three nations--Windurst, Bastok and San d'Oria--sent an expedition to investigate this cursed land.
1�The Galka swordsman Raogrimm, the Hume monk Cornelia, the Hume warrior Ulrich...
1�The Elvaan knight Francmage, the Tarutaru white mage Iru-Kuiru, and the Mithra ranger Rabntah were the members of the expedition.
1�All of them were great heroes of their people. But they had to cut the expedition short when an accident claimed two of their group.
1�Raogrimm and Cornelia were the ones who died in the accident. The others are said to have suffered violent deaths themselves after their return.
1�Perhaps they had awakened the curse that was said to be buried in this land... They may have called forth the ancient bane.
1�His image?I see...
1�??The great bane will devour the fair land of Vana'diel...??
1�??The ancient seal will be broken, awakening nightmares of ages past.??
1�??The blood of innocents will soak the earth, and the world will fall into fear and despair.??
1�Just an old wives' tale. I do not know why I mentioned it.I must go. I do not expect to find much, but something troubles me...
1�The door seems to be locked from the other side.
1�Pass through the door?Yes.No.
1�However, it's as I thoughtaru...Ze magique zat you have brought to moi has been half-erased by some strange power.
1�If you battle certain magical creatures, it may have an adverse effectaru on zat magique tome.
1�Ah! You've succeeded! C'est magnifique!Finally, you have brought moi ze magique completely intactaru.Merci!
1�Ah! You've succeeded! C'est magnifique!We've had all sorts of bother-wother trying to get Doctor Shantotto's magique here intact.
1�I'm really quite busy-wusy studying zis golem at ze momentaru.If you have something to say to moi, say it tout suite.
1�I never expected to see you here again...You adventurers certainly get around.
1�...And now what of zee Book of zee Gods? What has become of it since zee ancient restored its magic?
1�...I see.Zee Star Sibyl has yet to forgive Ajido-Marujido...
1�If she is really zat furious......It's possible zee Star Sibyl intends to quash all traces of Ajido-Marujido's natural-born magical ability.
1�Zee Dark Dungeon has zat kind of power. In my student days, I saw with my own eyes one who had met with such a fate.
1�.....And how is poor Apururu holding up?She mustaru be worrying herself sick.
1�And zat is zee course of action she has decided on?...Such a brave girl.
1�Well, zen.You must take my 3???? and return to Windurst. Please help our dear Apururu.
1�Take zee Book of zee Gods to Ajido-Marujido. He is not one to shrink back in zee face of zee truth.
1�What is this? You are here to complete my task for me?
1�So, Michea and Gwill are...However, I don't understand why you're here. Are you a new student?
1�Whatever the reason... Let me inform you of what our master would like accomplished.
1�In one of the Orc settlements in Davoi, 6???? can be found.You must enter one of their tents to find it.
1�Our master wants us to bring this to him. What, you ask, is this item for?Only our master can answer that question. However, I think it may have to do with my sisters...
1�At any rate, that is all I know.As for me, I am going to take our master's advice and rest at my home on the Kulatz Bridge.
1�Dark... So dark...I can't...move...Somebody...free me from this place...Free me from this darkness...
1�I still have something I need to tell her...
1�You throw in 6???? and give a moment of silence for the spirits of the beasts.
1�You throw in 6???? and give a moment of silence for the spirits of the beasts.
1�Your futile attempts at respect are nothing but self-gratifying actions.Do you think that throwing 6???? in this pond will bring the beasts back?Do you think they will be appeased?
1�Have you ever stopped to think why it's always the people who survive and the beasts that die?
1�Only I can relieve them of their true pain--and that is through revenge.You understand my words, do you not?
1�My pet was taken from me and my body left unable to perform my act.I cannot forgive what has come upon me.
1�I ask you for your assistance.I will be waiting for your answer the next time we meet, but I already know you will help me.
1�You are late.Is something wrong? You look as if you are confused by my being here.
1�If you must know, I could not allow my brother to be involved in this.
1�I am not inclined to inform Narcheral, but the white mages from the cathedral have been deployed into the surrounding area. Any further assembly of monsters has been prevented.
1�All that remains is to quell the rage of the marquis.
1�Jeronne, inform the adventurer what ?[he/she] needs to know. I am going to check on our backup.
1�What of your knights, Brother?
1�My brother...
1�Do not be foolish. I have already seen the light--the light of victory which shines down upon you.
1�It is the least I can do for my noble brother...
1�I will be here waiting for your return!
1�He is such a kind man.I was ordered to keep my opinions to myself...but I know that this decision was made with Prince Trion in mind.
1�The Prince looks fine, but the truth is that his wounds are not healing well.
1�However, if Prince Trion learned of the situation that unfolded in Tavnazia, he would more than likely wish to lead the forces onto the battlefield himself.
1�The reason Prince Pieuje is keeping this operation a secret is solely for the well-being of Prince Trion.
1�I apologize. I have been rambling... Let me inform you on our latest report.It seems as if the #???? possessed by dark stalkers is the signal for assembly.
1�Now, the barrier is prohibiting the assembly. Now is the perfect time to purify the marquis' soul.Use the #???? and find a place suitable for calling him forth.

1�The details of this operation are strictly to have adventurers proceed in advance. When the soul has been purified, take back the proof of your success to Narcheral and we will continue from there.
1�May the Goddess protect you in Her mercy...
1�Again, I apologize for the length of my speech, but there is one more thing.Narcheral is not rushing the situation. He and I were raised in different monasteries.
1�And those two monasteries have been destroyed by the Orcs.We both have the same wish in our hearts... But we do not want to lose anything more.
1�Understood. You may step down.It looks as though this conflict is to be decided in the arena.
1�Noble knights of San d'Oria! If you fear for your lives, you are free to return to your families. However, unless the Orcs are defeated here today, you may not have a home to return to.
1�Those who wish to stay, entrust your lives to me, and I will not let you, your families, nor our fine kingdom down.
1�Let us take back what the beasts have wrongfully stolen from us! Let us bring victory to the San d'Orian people!
1�My company will enter the arena and attempt to locate the central command.
1�Do not be ridiculous, Rahal. I have a duty to my kingdom and the countless lives that reside within it. And even if I am to fall in battle, Pieuje will be there to replace me.
1�Knights, take your positions! The time for judgment is upon us! And may victory taste as sweet as the Rolanberry 813 we shall drink when we return home!
1�Curilla?
1�As I expect yours.
1�Be silent, Pieuje, for I know that which you wish to say.Support the frontline, and take care of San d'Oria when that time comes.
1�Your words have given me strength, Pieuje. I thank you.
1�Take care, Pieuje!
1�Prince Trion.
1�There are still matters between us that are yet to be settled. I expect your prompt and safe return...
1�Prince Trion! That would be suicide! Assign the task to my knights!
